14. The Board may from time to time make rules, not inconsistent
with this Act or any approved scheme or regulations made thereunder,
for  all  or  any  of  the  following  purposes:

(f) the  method  of  accounting  as  between  the  Board,  turf
clubs and totalizator agencies in respect of investments,
dividends  and  commission;

(a) receives or permits to be received any investment on the
totalizator  in  respect  of  any  race  after  the  start  of  such
race;

(c) takes  into  account  in  the  calculation  or  payment  of  any
dividend  any  investment  which  has  not  been  publicly
registered on the totalizator in accordance with this section;
